  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class ProfilerFrame
implements AutoCloseable

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      List<ProfilerFrame> Children
      The children of this frame
      int ChildrenElapsedTime
      Elapsed time in millis spent in childen of this frame
      boolean Closed
      True if the frame has been closed and is no longer on the stack, false if the frame is open and is still on the stack.
      int ElapsedTime
      Amount of time in millis that the frame was open, difference between pop time and push time, this includes all the elapsed time of children; -1 if the frame is still on the stack ("open")
      int FrameTime
      Amount of time spent in this frame, does not include the elapsed time of children; ; -1 if the frame is still on the stack ("open")
      int NumChildren
      Number of children for this frame.
      int Offset
      Time in millis from when the stack started to when this frame was pushed on to the stack
      ProfilerFrame Parent
      Parent of this frame; NULL if this frame has a depth of 0
      String Path
      Get path from root
      Map<String,Object> PropertiesAndCounters
      A map of all the properties and counters, hashed by name
      ProfilerTag Tag
      Identifier of the frame; doesn't have to be unique
